reviewText: As before, a little weird for me

I expected better than I got. While there are a few not-bad segments, the series overall is utter rubbish. Nothing scary about it -- too much gratuitous violence and nudity for my taste. Too bad I can't return this!
Picked up the DVD's on a whim (season 1 and 2 together) and really enjoyed them. They were shipped quickly and in my grubby little paws faster then expected
